  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_3674884d-21d8-4842-80a3-f32e6d9c5648" class="text-block-content">
    <p>View the content created in the Rich Content Editor.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
